                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270531-197-off1046 t18270531-197-crimeloc1049"></join>. On the 10th of May I was at a public-house opposite my shop - Mrs. Mason, my lodger, alarmed me; I came out, and and met the prisoner running from my house, with the books, which had been on a shelf at the window.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270531-197-person1117">
